Citation.sTitle: Densities and Viscosities of Binary Mixtures of Tri-n-butyl Phosphate + Cyclohexane, + n-Heptane at T ) (288.15, 293.15, 298.15, 303.15, and 308.15) K
Citation.sAbstract: Densities and viscosities of binary mixtures of tri-n-butyl phosphate with cyclohexane and n-heptane have  been measured over the entire range of compositions at T ) (288.15, 293.15, 298.15, 303.15, and 308.15)  K and atmospheric pressure. The viscosity data have been represented by the Grunberg-Nissan equation.
